   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         <pb facs="yal.00103.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
         
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <name type="place">Boston,</name> 
                  <date when="1863-10-14">Oct 14, 1863</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Walt Whitman</salute>
           
                  <salute>Dear Friend&#8212;</salute>
               
            </opener>
         <p>About the Book&#8212;yes, if I<ptr target="yal.00103_n100"/> can. I wd like to have it sent on &amp; I will see what I can do about it. Dependent on others for capital, I can't answer any questions of will you publish? right off either yes or no.</p>
            <p>Glad to know you are now in good running trim; I will do all I can here, in one direction, to keep you supplied with funds.</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>You<gap reason="illegible" extent="1-2 letters"/> 
                  <gap reason="illegible"/>
               </salute>
               <signed>James Redpath</signed>
            </closer>
         
         <pb facs="yal.00103.002.jpg" type="verso"/>
      </body>
